│ special case.\n\n**File**: `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp`\n\n**Edit     │
│ Point**: Lines 10396-10406\n\n**Proposed Code**:\n\n```cpp\n      // If the main vector    │
